core.name: seed
core.description: ID of the object from which to start

core.name: association
core.description: The association to traverse. Can be either an association or association kind.

core.name: direction
core.description: Direction to traverse. Valid values BOTH, IN, OUT

core.name: removeDuplicateAggregateLinks
core.description: Duplicate aggregate links are somtimes created by scanners, when set to true they will not be displayed in responses.

core.name: depth
core.description: Depth of traversal. Valid values [0,N). 0 means traverse fully, any other integer means return links upto N hops from the seed node.

core.name: includeTerms
core.description: If  true, connected business terms will be embedded in the response.

core.name: includeAttribute
core.description: Facts with the given attribute id will be embedded in the response.

core.name: q
core.description: Search query to match objects. [Lucene Query Syntax](https://lucene.apache.org/core/2_9_4/queryparsersyntax.html)

core.name: related
core.description: Return related objects, q must also be specified
